@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp / wp.sin(0.71))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp))
    v2 = (0.35 + wp.exp(0.71))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.92)) / ((v1 + 0.51 / v1 + 0.07) + (v0 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.11)))
    tmp = v2
    data[tid] = v0
